<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.7">
<l>potta vuralaik kaviḻttataṉ mēlēṟi</l>
<l>tittit tapālum taṭāviṉil veṇṇeyum</l>
<l>mettat tiruvayi ṟāra viḻuṅkiya</l>
<l>vattaṉvan teṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">āḻiyāṉ eṉṉaip puṟampulkuvāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The Lord who, having turned over the perforated mortar</l>
<l>[and] climbed atop it, devoured [all] the sweet milk</l>
<l>and the butter in pots so that [his] holy stomach was very full,</l>
<l>comes, he will embrace me from behind.</l>
<l>He with the discus will embrace me from behind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
